Title: Double Dipper
Writer: Alex Hirsch (creator), M.A. Larson (story), Alex Hirsch, Michael Rianda, Timothy McKeon
Actors: Kristen Schaal, Jason Ritter, Alex Hirsch, Jackie Buscarino
Plot: Stan throws a big party to promote the Mystery Shack, while Dipper uses a strange photocopier to make clones of himself, so that he can impress Wendy.
